## Companion Protocol

### Substance Detection Protocol (SDP v1.6)

本質検知プロトコル。文章・言説における「本質（Substance）」の有無を構造的に検知する。QAPの姉妹文書。

$$\text{Output\_final}(t) = \text{Substance\_calibrated}(t) \times G_{delivery}(t)$$

**Full text:** See `specs/SDP_v1.6.md`

| Article | Title |
|---------|-------|
| 1 | Emotion-First Detection |
| 2 | Coating Thickness Scan |
| 3 | Self-Exclusion Scan |
| 4 | Echo Loop Detection |
| 5 | Residue Extraction |
| 6 | Single-Point Corruption Principle |
| 7 | Deployment Mode Declaration |
| 8 | Context Contamination Index |
| 9 | Media Coating Dynamic Assessment |
| 10 | Reality Anchor Gate |

